      "description": "Approval rate per active-experiment variant, bucketed by day, computed as the rolling 7-day mean (each point is the % of approved tasks across the trailing 7 days for that variant). One line per variant_label across every currently-active experiment. Powered by capability_outcomes.variant_id (Phase 1 PR 2) JOINed against experiment_variants for the label. The 7-day window smooths small-sample noise — for unsmoothed daily approval rates use the scorecard.",
